title: Seattle Web Design Firm efelle creative Ranks as the 23rd Fastest Growing Private Company in Washington
text:
For the second consecutive year, efelle creative was named to the Puget Sound Business Journal’s list of fastest-growing private companies in the state.
Seattle, Washington (PRWEB) October 22, 2015
Seattle-based efelle creative , a web firm specializing in award-winning, custom website design and development for businesses, ranked 23rd on the Puget Sound Business Journal’s list of the 100 Fastest Growing Private Companies in Washington, moving up from last year’s ranking of 98th. The annual list is compiled from more than 1,000 nominees across the state and was featured in the publication's October 8th issue.
“We are honored to be recognized again this year as one of Washington’s fastest-growing businesses,” says efelle creative co-founder and CEO, Fred Lebhart. “We fully attribute our continued growth and success to long-term client partnerships and our team’s ability to deliver an unparalleled client experience. We take the time to fully understand the demands of our clients’ businesses, and we create responsive websites with award-winning designs and custom, often complex, functionality.”
The efelle team’s hard work is getting noticed, as this ranking falls on the heels of another achievement for the company. Earlier this year, efelle creative was named as one of Inc. 5000s Fastest-Growing Companies of 2015, joining the national ranks of previous honorees such as Go-Pro, Microsoft, Zappos, Zillow, Jamba Juice, and Oracle.
More than 600 clients nationwide have partnered with efelle’s highly-experienced team of developers, designers, internet marketing professionals, and production and support staff to create customized websites and complete online marketing systems. The team at efelle continues to produce award-winning work, emerging as a leader in the industry and one of the fastest growing private companies in the country.
About efelle creative:
efelle creative is an award-winning digital agency based in Seattle, WA USA. We offer a broad range of online marketing services including web design, web development, eCommerce services, SEO services, email marketing, and cloud hosting. Founded in Seattle in 2005, efelle is a one-stop shop for small to medium businesses interested in improving their business via online marketing. With more than 40 creative professionals servicing over 600 clients across the country and even internationally, efelle is one of the fastest-growing private companies in the country. Contact us to learn more!
